column6: SPIDER-MAN, BLACK WIDOW, KITTY, CLOAK & DAGGER barely hold back the carnage of vengeful sewer leaders AGENT CROCK & VERMIN! - The BENGAL joins the police squad just in time to regulate Scourge's murderous aftermath! - Will the hunt for CROSSBONES reveal a deeper, darker secret behind the city's rampant crime wave?
column8: | writer:Michel Fiffe | artist:Giannis Milonogiannis | penciller (cover):David Nakayama
